# Designs

---

## UiSystem-D1 Responsive 3-Zone Layout System
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/App.vue`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** —

| Breakpoint | Zone A | Zone B | Zone C |
|---|---|---|---|
| `≥1280px` | 220px sidebar | flex main | 280–320px context |
| `1024–1279px` | 220px sidebar | flex main | hidden, toggle drawer |
| `<1024px` | tab nav | full main | bottom sheet |

```css
.autoforge-app {
  display: flex;
  height: 100vh;
}
.view-rail { width: 180px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.view-main { flex: 1; display: flex; min-width: 0; }
```



