#### 3. AgentsConfigView.vue — New Integration (~30 strings)

**File**: `frontend/src/views/AgentsConfigView.vue` (902 lines)

Already has `useI18n` imported with partial `t()` calls for `agents.createAgent`, `common.default`, `common.edit`, `common.upload`, `common.generate`, `common.generating`, `common.remove`, `agents.agentName`, `agents.agentNamePlaceholder`, `agents.profession`, `agents.soul`, `agents.soulPlaceholder`, `agents.soulHint`, `agents.apiSource`, `agents.modelTier`, `agents.equippedSkills`. Remaining hardcoded:

```vue
<!-- BEFORE: -->
<h2>Agent Forge</h2>
<button @click="handleResetDefaults">Reset Defaults</button>
<button @click="startCreate"><Plus :size="14" /> Create Agent</button>
<div class="agents-empty">Loading agents...</div>
<p>No agents configured. Reset defaults to get started.</p>
<summary>Advanced Settings</summary>
<label>Temperature ({{ editing.temperature.toFixed(1) }})</label>
<label>Max Tokens</label>
<label>Reasoning Budget</label>
<span>Thinking Mode</span>
<div class="form-hint">Enable Claude extended thinking for deeper reasoning.</div>
<label>Thinking Budget ({{ editing.thinking_budget ?? 0 }})</label>
```

**Script changes** — replace `alert()` and `confirm()`:

```typescript
// BEFORE:
alert('ID and Name are required')
confirm('Delete this agent?')
confirm('Reset to default agents? Custom agents will be lost.')

// AFTER:
alert(t('agents.idNameRequired'))
confirm(t('agents.deleteConfirm'))
confirm(t('agents.resetConfirm'))
```

**Translation keys to add** (~13 keys):

| Key | en.json | zh.json |
|-----|---------|---------|
| `agents.title` | `"Agent Forge"` | `"智能体工坊"` |
| `agents.loading` | `"Loading agents..."` | `"加载智能体..."` |
| `agents.empty` | `"No agents configured. Reset defaults to get started."` | `"尚未配置智能体。重置默认值以开始使用。"` |
| `agents.advancedSettings` | `"Advanced Settings"` | `"高级设置"` |
| `agents.temperature` | `"Temperature ({value})"` | `"温度 ({value})"` |
| `agents.maxTokens` | `"Max Tokens"` | `"最大 Token 数"` |
| `agents.reasoningBudget` | `"Reasoning Budget"` | `"推理预算"` |
| `agents.thinkingMode` | `"Thinking Mode"` | `"思考模式"` |
| `agents.thinkingHint` | `"Enable Claude extended thinking for deeper reasoning."` | `"启用 Claude 扩展思考以获得更深层的推理。"` |
| `agents.thinkingBudget` | `"Thinking Budget ({value})"` | `"思考预算 ({value})"` |
| `agents.idNameRequired` | `"ID and Name are required"` | `"ID 和名称为必填项"` |
| `agents.deleteConfirm` | `"Delete this agent?"` | `"删除此智能体？"` |
| `agents.resetConfirm` | `"Reset to default agents? Custom agents will be lost."` | `"重置为默认智能体？自定义智能体将丢失。"` |

